channel.title: Antony Barja
channel.description: I am an Spatial Data Scientistic in development, working in infeccios diseases spatial modeling , spatial statistic and geovisualization inside Health Innovation Lab - Cayetano Heredia Peruvian, Lima-Peru. My primary research involves of the spatial data analysis and spatial - temporal modeling, addition the use different thecnology of geographic Information of open source and free. Please, feel free to browse my personal website and If you wish you can leave a comment.
